  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh, it's good to see you again! What's been on your mind today?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Been thinking about a new cricket game I watched last night. The final was too close! My team won by just one run. Was exciting."
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds thrilling — a one-run win is the best kind. What was the most exciting part for you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The final over was crazy. The last ball, the bowler took a wicket and gave a run. My team needed one run from 2 balls. The batsman hit a six. We all jumped! 🎉"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Right — a six on the last ball, what a finish! Did you root for the whole match or just the final over?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I was watching the whole match but got really tense in the last over. My friend and I were shouting at the screen! 😅"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That's the best kind of match — the kind that leaves you shouting! What will you watch next"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Not sure yet, but I might watch a Bollywood movie instead. I like to switch between cricket and movies. They’re very different but both chaar!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Chaar\" is a Hindi word I know — it means fun. What Bollywood movie are you in the mood for?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I was thinking of watching \"Pathaan\" again. It's an action movie with a lot of chaar moments and some cool stunts. Have you heard of it?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Right — Pathaan has some amazing action and fun moments. What part of the movie do you like best — the stunts, the songs, or something else?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The stunts are my favorite — they’re so over the top but done so well. But the songs are catchy too. I sing along sometimes, even if I don’t understand everything. 😄"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I get that — over-the-top stunts and catchy songs make for a perfect mix. Do you pick one song to sing the most?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The song \"Befikre\" I sing the most — it's so popular and easy to hum. Even my mom sings it sometimes! It’s from another movie, but I love it. Maybe I should watch that one again too."
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That’s a great song — fun and easy to hum. The movie *Befikre* is a good one to revisit. What made you like it the first time?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The story was light, the music was good, and the characters felt real. It’s the kind of movie that just makes you happy without trying too hard. Maybe I should watch it again this weekend. 😊"
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Light\" and \"real\" are exactly the kind of movies that stick with you. What’s your plan for the weekend besides watching movies?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I may go hiking with a friend or just relax at home. Work is busy, so I need to unwind. Maybe some cricket highlights too!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Right — busy work calls for a good unwind. Hiking or cricket highlights — which are you leaning toward?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 11,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hiking sounds nice, but I’m leaning toward relaxing at home this weekend. Just some snacks, movies, and maybe a quick game of cricket highlights later. Too much energy right now for hiking. 😊"
    },
    {
      "turn": 11,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Relaxing at home with snacks and movies sounds perfect. What’s your go-to snack for movie weekends?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 12,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Popcorn, obviously! Sometimes I add some garam masala and chaat masala for flavor — it’s my favorite. What about you? Do you have a movie snack?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 12,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Popcorn with garam masala and chaat masala — that’s brilliant! I’m a simple salt-and-butter person, honestly. Do you make it for every movie or just the good ones?"
    }
  ],
